title: Did any of you have trouble just GETTING your phone??
content: I have been waiting 1 Month and 3 days for my phone!! I ordered 2 Pixel 5 phones on January 9th--I received 1 phone on January 13th!!!! The other phone has not even been shipped yet!!! I have contacted Google at least 8 times and all I have been told is that "shipping specialists are working on it"!!!!!!!!!! That is all that they can tell me!
